BlogLatest
==========

o Introduction
o Installation
o Usage
o Configuration
o Donating
o More information

Introduction
------------
The BlogLatest widget lets you display the latest blog and wire posts from all users,
from certain users you choose or all your friends.You can put the widget on your
dashboard or profile. Simply edit the dashboard or profile page and drag the
"Latest Posts" to where you desire on the page.

Installation
------------
Download the zip file and extract to your Elgg mod directory and
enable the plugin in your Elgg's Tool Administration area.

Usage
-----
You can put the widget on your dashboard or profile.
Simply edit the dashboard or profile page and drag the "Latest Posts"
to where you desire on the page.

Configuration
-------------
If you click on the Edit link in the widget you can specify the user to follow or whether
to follow only your friends, the number of posts to display, 10 being the default,
the tags to use for filtering the latest blogs and also the length of the extract to display.
This has a default of 140 characters, ala Twitter. You can also choose to follow either blog
posts or wire posts, or both.

Donating
--------
If you use this plugin and find it useful, please think about donating something to
support the open source development of the plugin. Just go to the source code page:
http://github.com/codebrane/bloglatest
and click on Danate.
Thank you very much!

